query_params.endDate:
Only transactions before the End Date will be returned.
Note: The maximum date range is one year. Valid ISO-8601 formats are :
yyyy-MM-dd.
query_params.startDate:
Only transactions after the Start Date will be returned.
Note: The maximum date range is one year. Valid ISO-8601 formats are :
yyyy-MM-dd.
query_params.symbol: Only transactions with the specified symbol will be returned.
query_params.type: Only transactions with the specified type will be returned.
